{"id":18538,"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/06/61/66129.jpg","floor":"#1","group":"靠谱人生茶话会","groupHref":"/group/boring","groupThumb":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/icon/m/000/00/03/364.jpg","message":"温哥华9月3日星期一，接皇叔短讯，欲至Salmon House共进晚餐，偕洗衣机君与同游。<br>于是欣然前往。席定晚七点，三人<span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">会晤</span>面基甚欢。<br>公交车上，<span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">二人二目相对</span>（四目相对了啦！），言不尽之意，传脉脉之情。<br><img src=\"http://i1122.photobucket.com/albums/l536/GrubSt/IMG_20120902_193041.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br><span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">结果定了七点的位子，来到地方都几乎八点了，摔</span><br><br>皇叔兴奋不能自已。<br>三人共坐一席，窗外海风习习。放眼望去，波澜壮阔，鱼跃涛中。波光粼粼，渔火点点。夜幕沉沉，水天如墨。对岸火树银花，此边孤烛短檠。<br>上得菜来，捉刀举叉。洗衣机不喜海鲜，<br><img src=\"http://i1122.photobucket.com/albums/l536/GrubSt/Mosaiced.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br>皇叔则大快朵颐，开怀大嚼。<br><img src=\"http://i1122.photobucket.com/albums/l536/GrubSt/IMG_20120902_201652.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br><br>酒至酣处，猜枚行令，行欢作乐，无极不至<span style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">，无所不为。</span></span><br><img src=\"http://i1122.photobucket.com/albums/l536/GrubSt/IMG_20120902_205125.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br>既传眉目之情，又行交杯之礼，此乃面基之所指，Bangumi众之所归也。<br>餐后三人微醺，飘飘然各回各家各找各妈可也。<br>是为面基记。 ","time":"2012-9-5 06:40","title":"面基记","userId":"grubstreet","userName":"小寒","userSign":"(Idle singer of an empty day)"}